ctrl+alt+g - start gedit
alt+F12 - run command
 
alt+F1 - minimize window
alt+F2 - toggle maximize window
alt+F3 - toggle full screen
ctrl+alt+d - minimize all windows

ctrl+alt+F1 do F6 terminali
ctrl+alt+F7 do F12 xwindovi

ctrl+shift+c - copy in terminal
ctrl+shift+v - paste in terminal

explorer:
ctrl+l - location
ctrl+shift+n - new folder
ctrl+h - show hidden files

gedit:
ctrl+g - find the next instance of the string.
ctrl+shft+g - find the previous instance of the string. 
Ctrl+Shft+K - Clear highlight 

